title: War of the Roses: He Went from Prince Charming to Ghost Charming
description: Maggie is worried her boyfriend Lucas is up to something because he went from hanging out all the time and experiencing the honeymoon phase of a relationship to barely seeing him during the week real fast.  Is it because he's now seeing someone else?
